00:01:38.000 --> 00:01:50.000
<v Dorian (Dorian Williams)>
And! She's taken it … [action] We actually see jump over Black and White Minstrels chorus] She's over the Minstrels. She just flicked Leslie Crowther with her tail, but the time's good, and now she turns before coming into the final jump … this is a tough one … It's Ben-Hur - forty-six chariots … 6,000 spectators … 400 slaves, lion-handlers, the Emperor Nero and the entire Coliseum. 198 feet high. 400 years across!

00:01:50.000 --> 00:01:54.000
<v Mrs Mock Tudor>
I bet we don't see this one.

